item.description:
wontfix: <p>
As noted above, this can be done using <code>comment_class</code> filter if needed:
</p>
<pre class="wiki">function add_by_blog_user_class_16944( $classes, $class, $comment_id ) {
	$comment = get_comment( $comment_id );
	if ( ! is_multisite() || is_user_member_of_blog( $comment-&gt;user_id ) )
		$classes[] = 'by-blog-user';
	return $classes;
}
add_filter( 'comment_class', 'add_by_blog_user_class_16944', 10, 3 );
</pre>
